# Claude Code project-level tooling config (per-clone, not shared)
/.claude/

# AGENTS.md is a TRACKED, stable stub pointing agents to CLAUDE.md (see the file
# itself). The claude-mem plugin may overwrite the local working copy with a
# session memory dump; protect it per-clone with
# `git update-index --skip-worktree AGENTS.md` so those writes never get
# committed. Do NOT re-ignore it - it must ship in the repo.

